= Goddadka Xisaabta =

'''God-xisaabeed''' waa hab ama qaab ka mid ah [[cilmi]]ga [[xisaab]]ta lagu kala saaro godadka [[tiro]]oyinka. 

Tusaale ahaan [[tiro]]da [[todoba]] waxay ka mid tahay [[toban]]ka lambar ee la isku yidhaahdo '''Hal-godleey'''. Halka tirada [[konton]]-iyo-[[shan]] ka tirsan yahay [[Labo-god]]leeyda oo ugu dambeeyso [[sagaashan]]-iyo-[[sagaal]]. 


== Qeeybaha Goddadka Tirada ==

Goddadka [[tiro]]da lama soo koobi karo, laakiin waxaa u muhiimsan oo ugu horeeya kuwan hoos ku xusan:

* ''Hal-godleey'' = 0 - 9 oo loo yaqaano [[Kow]]aad. 

* ''Labo-godleey'' = 10 - 99 oo loo yaqaano [[Toban]]aad. 

* ''Sadex-godleey'' = 100 - 999 oo loo yaqaano [[Boqol]]aad. 

* ''Afar-godleey'' = 1'000 - 9'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Kun]]aad. 

* ''Shan-godleey'' = 10'000 - 99'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Toban]]-[[Kun]]aad. 

* ''Lix-godleey'' = 100'000 - 999'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Boqol]]-[[Kun]]aad. 

* ''Todoba-godleey'' = 1'000'000 - 9'999'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Milyan]]. 

* ''Sideed-godleey'' 10'000'000 - 99'999'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Toban]]-[[Milyan]]aad. 

* ''Sagaal-godleey'' 100'000'000 - 999'999'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Boqol]]-[[Milyan]]aad. 

* ''Toban-godleey'' 1'000'000'000 - 9'999'999'999 [[Bilyan]]aad. 

* ''Toban-iyo-kow-godleey'' 10'000'000'000 - 99'999'999'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Toban]]-[[Bilyan]]aad. 

* ''Toban-iyo-labo-godleey'' 100'000'000'000 - 999'999'999'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Boqol]]-[[Bilyan]]aad. 

* ''Toban-iyo-sadex-godleey'' 1'000'000'000'000 - 9'000'000'000'000 oo loo yaqaano [[Tiriliyan]]. 

* ''Toban-iyo-Afar-godleey'' 10'000'000'000'000 - 99'999'999'999'999 oo loo yaqaano [[Toban]]-[[Tiriliyan]]aad

* ''Toban-iyo-shan-godleey'' 100'000'000'000'000 - 999'999'999'999'999 oo lagu magacaabo [[Boqol]]-[[Tiriliyan]]aad. 


